<m0>Testing, testing: Abbott<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .33 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>starts search for cure<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 3.98 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.486 INCHES<m2><ql>
